author: Aaron Jones
description:
The third and final season of Squid Game has arrived and the international hit sensation about contestants fighting for survival in a series of deadly games for life changing money finishes on a high. The Korean continues Seong Gui-hun’s attempt at taking the games down from the inside and wraps up the core story whilst […]
